<title>USA: Platinum Software names Klaus chairman.</title>
<headline>Platinum Software names Klaus chairman.</headline>
<dateline>IRVINE, Calif. 1996-09-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Platinum Software Corp Tuesday said President and Chief Executive Officer George Klaus will assume the added responsibility of chairman of the board.</p>
<p>In a statement, the company said Carmelo Santoro has resigned as chairman but will remain on the board and serve as an advisor to Klaus.</p>
